## SDD Usage

Start a new change:
- `/sdd-new <change-name>` ‚Äî interactive, pauses between phases for confirmation
- `/sdd-ff <change-name>` ‚Äî fast-forward, runs all phases automatically
- `/sdd-continue <change-name>` ‚Äî resume an interrupted change from last completed phase

Initialize SDD in a project first: `/sdd-init`
